<tool id="SAGA.climate_tools.8" name="ETpot (after Hargreaves, Grid)" version="1.0.0"><description>Estimation of daily potential evapotranspiration from daily average, minimum and maximum temperatures using Hargreave's empirical equation. In order to estimate extraterrestrial net radiation geographic latitude of observation and Julian day have to be supplied too. </description><inputs><param name="T" label="Mean Temperature" help="Mean Temperature" type="text" format="image/tiff, application/x-ogc-envi, application/x-ogc-aaigrid, image/png" /><param name="T_MIN" label="Minimum Temperature" help="Minimum Temperature" type="text" format="image/tiff, application/x-ogc-envi, application/x-ogc-aaigrid, image/png" /><param name="T_MAX" label="Maximum Temperature" help="Maximum Temperature" type="text" format="image/tiff, application/x-ogc-envi, application/x-ogc-aaigrid, image/png" /><param name="LAT" label="Latitude [Degree]" help="Latitude [Degree]" type="float" format="image/tiff, application/x-ogc-envi, application/x-ogc-aaigrid, image/png" /><param name="TIME" label="Time" help="Time" type="text" format="image/tiff, application/x-ogc-envi, application/x-ogc-aaigrid, image/png" /><param name="MONTH" label="Month" help="Month" type="text" format="image/tiff, application/x-ogc-envi, application/x-ogc-aaigrid, image/png" /><param name="DAY" label="Day of Month" help="Day of Month" type="integer" format="image/tiff, application/x-ogc-envi, application/x-ogc-aaigrid, image/png" /></inputs><outputs><data name="PET" label="Potential Evapotranspiration" /></outputs></tool>